{"tid":1139471,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"波鞋放太耐唔著鞋底碎片化","createTime":"2019-05-05T09:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T12:58:42.000Z","uid":152298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"df86bf1eade802da7102216be4190cb2e3ad6868","tid":1139471,"uid":152298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:37:17.000Z","msg":"今日諗住拿對出來著下<br />\n抹完都無事<br />\n一躇上去行兩步鞋底就開始碎開<br />\n已經唔知第幾對係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無方法可以防止？"},{"pid":"14303d29600d815973ebbaf1110b9155021e53e1","tid":1139471,"uid":621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:38:37.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n間中拎出嚟著下"},{"pid":"b72afefef9bee4d781bba3396292b2bd36c9f0fc","tid":1139471,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:44:28.000Z","msg":"可以dom得<br />\n我屋企個對放左3年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca02ed44d46e6b50a55b01eefabdd8e38bdc6f7","tid":1139471,"uid":54455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:46:41.000Z","msg":"成日著有汗有水氣<br />\n反而著得耐"},{"pid":"d9e966687ff11587a7aa8b94c89dc82b26fa5d53","tid":1139471,"uid":92145,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:49:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUW2vSP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUW2vSP.jpg&h=265420a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"700bbccf06d43e6634aafbf1ca17397c128012e5","tid":1139471,"uid":92145,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:52:15.000Z","msg":"話說今日present ，成team人夾好著返套西裝，加埋通宵準備，諗住掂過碌蔗可以爆4<br />\n<br />\npresent個陣，坐前排D同學係咁笑，我即刻淆一淆睇睇份稿有咩問題，但咩問題都冇。如是者就繼續pre la，點知班同學越笑越大聲，我跟住同學視線望落去。<br />\n<br />\n仆街!成地Oreo碎...&nbsp;<br />\n再望真D，原來係groupmate個鞋底碎曬<br />\n唔知係唔係前排D同學笑得太大聲<br />\n懷疑groupmate惱羞成怒，present緊個陣爆seed講左句屌你老母，係前門衝左出班房，剩返個鞋碎係到<br />\n成班靜曬，miss呆左，我都唔知點算好，坐前排笑最大聲果個嚇到O曬<br />\n三秒之後，個groupmate係後門入返黎，坐返自己位。<br />\n原來佢翻翻去換鞋，之後又走翻出黎，好怒咁踢左下堆鞋碎，然後死死氣咁執翻啲鞋碎入垃圾桶。<br />\n<br />\n落堂之後條友即刻衝走左，全班人走出去逐個逐個影塊地，睇翻原來黑到仆街<br />\n<br />\n準備左咁耐既Project，今次實爛Grad啦唉"},{"pid":"6cce2f4c5c54a203b62ce1ddb0729e4667ff5e4b","tid":1139471,"uid":144567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d9e966687ff11587a7aa8b94c89dc82b26fa5d53","tid":1139471,"uid":92145,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:49:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUW2vSP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUW2vSP.jpg&h=265420a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:52:25.000Z","msg":"成地Oreo個故仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccfe898146e320556c84abee9df5d401d76e984b","tid":1139471,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d9e966687ff11587a7aa8b94c89dc82b26fa5d53","tid":1139471,"uid":92145,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:49:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUW2vSP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUW2vSP.jpg&h=265420a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc6eb6bc69480b0b5c945ccbf42d1dd79177f92","tid":1139471,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T10:31:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fa763b85f1b629eee3820e57b6a8b11db7fdb2f","tid":1139471,"uid":58147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T10:36:46.000Z","msg":"以前啲Air max好耐都冇著，<br />\n之後一著出街就成個鞋底碎哂。"},{"pid":"546e02ca1b38236856e87edc56aa9ea8683983b1","tid":1139471,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T10:40:01.000Z","msg":"歐洲嘢，啲膠加咗環保分解劑，好彩嘅三年就爛，之前ben屎寶馬入便啲天花呔盆爛鳩曬都係咁。"},{"pid":"37